root = true

[*]
charset = utf-8
end_of_line = lf
insert_final_newline = true
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2

[*.{java,py}]
indent_size = 4

[*.md]
trim_trailing_whitespace = false
```

### .gitignore
```
# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# Dependencies（言語に合わせて追記）
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.gradle/
build/
target/

# Environment
.env
.env.local

# Logs
*.log